about.title: Information About me
about.infos: Hello, I'm Amin Mohamed an adept software developer boasting 3 years of hands-on experience. My coding arsenal features Java, Spring Boot, TypeScript, JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and Git CI/CD,and I find my stride in unraveling intricate problems. I'm driven by a fervor for staying abreast of industry trends and thrive in the camaraderie of diverse teams. Beyond my professional pursuits, I'm a devoted contributor to open-source initiatives, constantly seeking fresh challenges. Let's connect and embark on a journey to enhance your projects together.
